  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/imagecapturecore\/iccameraitemmetadataoption\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T21:38:17Z\n---\n\n# ICCameraItemMetadataOption\n\n**Structure**\n\nAn option for the item’s metadata.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstruct ICCameraItemMetadataOption\n```\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Requesting Metadata\n\n- **requestMetadata()**: Requests metadata for the item.\n- **metadata**: The item’s metadata.\n- **metadataIfAvailable**: The item’s metadata if it is readily available.\n- **flushMetadataCache()**: Deletes the item’s cached metadata.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
